Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on facial expression recognition using deep learning approaches, which is a subfield of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed Multi-Region Ensemble CNN framework is a machine learning approach that aims to enhance the learning power of CNN models. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep learning approaches to recognize facial expressions, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper uses facial expression databases that contain multimedia data (images and videos) to evaluate the proposed method. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper investigates the effects of different sub-regions of the whole face on facial expression recognition, which is related to human-computer interaction.
